{"type": "article", "id": 22446, "title": "有浮雕效果的瓷砖", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-18T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161338aLU3iZOfKy9kWw46.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">德国设计师 Konstantin Grcic 曾与意大利瓷砖品牌 Mutina 合作了一组瓷砖设计，一共有 6 种花纹。每种瓷砖都有几何式的图案，一部分经过上釉，另一部分是粗糙的，它们之间有了深浅的变化，像是图像上的阴影。Numini 的型号比 Numi 更小，在瓷砖表面以浮雕的手法制作，排列后也有光影的效果。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161335rEo6PcdtHMzZ81Jh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161336CeOD7WTv1Ljh95Jq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161336HMEfacpBdsZIk6WC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161337KyhbC5HqrGg1SdmE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161337uDBNehFAdRxPUlK5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}